🚀 Brevity – Short, Smart, Straight to the Point
Stay informed effortlessly with real-time news, smooth navigation, and a personalized reading experience — all in one powerful Flutter app.

📱 App Overview
Brevity is a multi-platform news reader app that brings you the latest headlines with features like infinite scrolling, bookmarking, theming, and full-article access. Powered by Flutter and Firebase with seamless UI/UX.

