🚀 Brevity – Short, Smart, Straight to the Point Stay informed effortlessly with real-time news, smooth navigation, and a personalized reading experience — all in one powerful Flutter app.
📱 App Overview
Brevity is a multi-platform news reader app that brings you the latest headlines with features like infinite scrolling, bookmarking, theming, and full-article access. Powered by Flutter and Firebase with seamless UI/UX.

🎬 Demo Videos
✨ Feature Area 🎥 Video Preview
Login & Sign Up Video 1 here
Main App Features Video 2 here
Additional Features Video 3 here

🌟 Core Features
🔄 Infinite Scrolling – No end to your feed!

📚 Side Navigation – Bookmark, access settings, and more

🎨 Theme Customization – Light/Dark mode support

🌐 Full Article Access – Open full stories in the browser

🔍 Search – Find news by category or keyword

🤝 One-Click Sharing – Share news with share_plus

⚙️ Technical Highlights
⚡ State Management: flutter_bloc

🚦 Navigation: go_router

📶 Caching: cached_network_image

🎬 UI/UX: Shimmer loading, smooth transitions

🏗️ Modular Architecture: Easy to scale and maintain

🛠️ Tech Stack
Layer Technologies Used
Frontend Flutter, Dart, Bloc
Backend Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Functions)
APIs News API, Gemini API
Storage Shared Preferences
IDE VS Code, Android Studio
Versioning Git

📦 Key Dependencies
flutter_bloc, go_router, cached_network_image, shimmer

firebase_auth, cloud_firestore, firebase_core

google_sign_in, http, intl, url_launcher

shared_preferences, flutter_dotenv, share_plus

card_swiper, showcaseview, gap, equatable

📁 Folder Structure

├── android/ # Android configuration
├── ios/ # iOS config files
├── linux/ | macos/ | windows/ | web/ # Platform support
├── assets/ # Images, logos
├── lib/ # Flutter source (views, models, controllers)
├── server/ # Node.js + MongoDB backend (in-progress)
├── test/ # Unit & widget tests
├── pubspec.yaml # Dependencies
├── .env # Environment variables
🚀 Installation & Setup
🧰 Prerequisites
Flutter SDK (v3.29.2+)

Dart SDK (v3.7.2+)

Git

Android Studio or VS Code with Flutter plugin

Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Yash159357/BREVITY
cd brevity

Install dependencies
flutter pub get
🔐 Configure Environment

touch .env
Add this to .env:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
NEWS_API_KEY=your_news_api_key_here
🔑 Obtain keys from:

Google AI Studio

NewsAPI.org

🔥 Firebase Setup
Go to Firebase Console

Add your Android/iOS app

Download:

google-services.json → android/app/

GoogleService-Info.plist → ios/Runner/

▶️ Run the App

flutter run # Debug mode
flutter run --release # Release mode
